      <title>泰国寻求通过五年税收减免扭转人才流失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/thailand-seeks-to-reverse-brain-drain-with-five-year-tax-breaks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国为吸引电子、汽车、机器人和航空等行业的人才，将把愿意回国为公司工作的专业人士的个人所得税税率削减约 50%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/thailand-seeks-to-reverse-brain-drain-with-five-year-tax-breaks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 07:25:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
